      passage:`Classes available for ages 6 months to 16 years. All lessons 30 minutes.\n\nLevels:\n• Tadpoles (6 months–3 years): parent must enter water\n• Frogs (3–5 years): teacher-led, no parent in water\n• Dolphins (6–12 years): independent swimming\n• Sharks (13–16 years): stroke technique and fitness\n\nPayment: Full term fees (10 weeks) due at enrolment. No refunds for missed classes — catch-up lessons available on request.\n\nPlease disclose any medical conditions at enrolment.`,
